# - Find the SciPy libraries
# This module finds if SciPy is installed, and sets the following variables
# indicating where it is.
#
#
#  SCIPY_FOUND               - was NumPy found
#  SCIPY_VERSION             - the version of NumPy found as a string
#  SCIPY_VERSION_MAJOR       - the major version number of NumPy
#  SCIPY_VERSION_MINOR       - the minor version number of NumPy
#  SCIPY_VERSION_PATCH       - the patch version number of NumPy
#  SCIPY_VERSION_DECIMAL     - e.g. version 1.6.1 is 10601
#  SCIPY_INCLUDE_DIRS        - path to the NumPy include files

